            <title><![CDATA[下午察：碧桂园杨氏父女跑路？]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<div class="figure-media"><img class="img-fluid lazyload" data-src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/articles/2023/10/19/2023-08-23T012228Z405390412RC22Q2AO4FXMRTRMADP3CHINA-PROPERTY-DEBT-COUNTRY-GARDEN3_0.jpg?VersionId=uFZ4kZQefcQ8H0ie8Zm.Z_7jSqbw2jFK&amp;itok=nfo5MUfT" title="陷入财务困境的地产巨头碧桂园首次面临境外违约之际，坊间传出其创始人杨国强及女儿杨惠妍跑路的消息。（路透社）" alt="陷入财务困境的地产巨头碧桂园首次面临境外违约之际，坊间传出其创始人杨国强及女儿杨惠妍跑路的消息。（路透社）" src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/articles/2023/10/19/2023-08-23T012228Z405390412RC22Q2AO4FXMRTRMADP3CHINA-PROPERTY-DEBT-COUNTRY-GARDEN3_0.jpg?VersionId=uFZ4kZQefcQ8H0ie8Zm.Z_7jSqbw2jFK&amp;itok=nfo5MUfT" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div> <figcaption>陷入财务困境的地产巨头碧桂园首次面临境外违约之际，坊间传出其创始人杨国强及女儿杨惠妍跑路的消息。（路透社）</figcaption>      <p>中国地产巨头恒大创始人许家印上月中秋之际被官宣采取强制措施后，中国地产大佬们的日子越发不好过。</p><p>随着同样陷入财务困境的另一地产巨头碧桂园首次面临境外违约，其创始人杨国强及女儿杨惠妍跑路的消息也甚嚣尘上。</p><p>碧桂园三度辟谣碧桂园六天内两度发文，展示杨国强在碧桂园项目的工作状态，试图破除市场传闻，但收效甚微。</p><div class="article-microtransaction"><div class="cta-subscribe">请<a href="https://subscribe.sph.com.sg/zh/promotions/zbpe-3-months-99-cents-promotion/?utm_campaign=zbpe399&amp;utm_medium=sph-publication&amp;utm_source=paywall-zb&amp;utm_content=subscribelink-pay-endofarticle" target="_blank"><span class="link link-underline">订阅</span></a>或<span href="javascript:;" onclick="_mySPHObj.openLogin()" id="paywall-login" class="link link-underline">登录</span>，以继续阅读全文！</div></div><style>.cta-subscribe {
